data.description: This beautiful newly renovated 3/2 lakefront home within a gated community is the largest model home in San Marco. It includes an eat- in kitchen with new appliances, a large living area, garage, and a large sunroom. New laminate flooring throughout (Except front guest bedroom, which is carpeted, bathrooms and laundry room are tiled). Accordion hurricane shutters on all windows. The master suite includes a walk-in closet and sliding glass doors leading to the sunroom. The master bathroom has two sinks, roman tub, shower, and makeup vanity. Nearby you will find a golf course, shopping center with Publix, and parks. The monthly HOA payment includes cable, Internet, exterior painting of the home, landscaping, Irrigation, roof cleaning, Manager on Site, Renovated Clubhouse and ADT monitoring.
